uCareSystem for Debian
======================

This package provides the uCareSystem maintenance tool for Debian-based systems.

Installation Notes:
- The package automatically configures the Utappia repository
- GPG keys are retrieved automatically during installation
- The tool supports Ubuntu, Debian, and derivatives

Usage:
- Run `sudo ucaresystem-core` for full maintenance
- Use `ucaresystem-core --help` for available options
- Desktop launcher available in Applications menu

Configuration:
- Repository: ppa:utappia/stable
- GPG keyring: /etc/apt/keyrings/utappia-archive-keyring.gpg

For support, visit: https://github.com/Utappia/uCareSystem